# Production environment (Phase 6)
# These are BUILD-TIME variables (Vite inlines `VITE_`-prefixed vars into the
# client bundle). Set them in the Vercel dashboard → Project → Settings →
# Environment Variables (Production), then redeploy.
#
# SECURITY: only the Supabase ANON key may live here — it is meant to be public
# (RLS protects data). NEVER put the service-role key or the Anthropic API key in
# any VITE_ variable; those stay server-side (the Anthropic key lives only in
# Supabase Edge Function secrets).

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here
